<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('head') %>
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="logo-filters pt-3">
        <div class="logo mt-2 mb-3">
            <img src="images/logo.png" class="rounded-circle" height="70" alt="image">
            <a href="/">
                <h1 class="m-0 mt-3 ml-2">Film Buff</h1>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="search-filters">
            <div class="filters mt-5 mx-5">
                <p class="sort" value="18">DRAMA</p>
                <p class="sort" value="10749">ROMANCE</p>
                <p class="sort" value="28">ACTION</p>
                <p class="sort" value="35">COMEDY</p>
                <p class="sort" value="27">HORROR</p>
                <p id="more" class="mr-0">MORE</p>
            </div>
            <form class="form" action="/get-movie-results/:title/:page">
                <div class="search-box mt-4 mx-2">
                    <input type="text" name="searchBox" id="searchBox" placeholder="Search...">
                    <button class="btn " type="submit" id="searchButton">
                        <i class="fa fa-search search-icon"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="more-filters ">
        <p class="filter-options" value="12">Adventure</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="16">Animation</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="80">Crime</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="99">Documentary</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="10751">Family</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="14">Fantasy</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="36">History</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="9648">Mystery</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="878">Science Fiction</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="53">Thriller</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="filter-options" value="37">Western</p>
    </div>
    <div class="results-container">
    </div>
    <div class="pagination-container text-center"></div>
    <div id="carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="item active">
                <img src="images/drama.jpg" alt="Los Angeles" style="width:100%;">
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="images/romantic.jpg" alt="Chicago" style="width:100%;">
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="images/action.webp" alt="New york" style="width:100%;">
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="images/comedy.jpg" alt="New york" style="width:100%;">
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="images/horror.jpg" alt="New york" style="width:100%;">
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel" data-slide="next">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="about-application">
        <h3 class="text-center"><strong>Discover Your next cinematic adventure with our movie search
                application!</strong></h3>
        <p>Are you in the mood for thrilling action, heartwarming romance, mindobending sci-fi, or perhaps a good
            old-fashioned comedy? Look no further ! Our movie search application is your ultimate movie companion,
            designed to help you find the perfect film for every mood and occasion.Movie Buff is not just a movie search
            application; it's a complete movie lover's ecosystem. Whether you're a fan of action, romance, sci-fi, or
            indie films, Movie Buff empowers you to explore the world of cinema like never before. Discover, share, and
            experience the magic of movies with Movie Buff today. Your next movie adventure is just a search away!
        </p>
        <hr>
        <div class="application-descriptions">
            <div class="powerful-sort mr-4">
                <h4 id="powerfulSortHeading" class="text-center"><strong>Powerful Sort</strong></h4>
                <div class="powerful-sort-content">
                    <p>Sort your search results by factors like popularity, release date, or user ratings, helping you
                        find the perfect movie that suits your current mood and preferences</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="movie-details mr-3">
                <h4 id="movieDetailsHeading" class="text-center"><strong>Movie Details</strong></h4>
                <div class="movie-details-content">
                    <p>Unlock the Magic of Cinema with a Single Click! Discover Movie Details Instantly. Say goodbye to
                        the hassle of searching for movie information. Just click on the title, and embark on a
                        cinematic journey.The power of knowledge is just a click away!"</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="Search">
                <h4 id="searchheading" class="text-center"><strong>Search</strong></h4>
                <div class="search-content p-0">
                    <p>Just put the movie name and click the search button, and that's how you can find the movie with
                        our application.You can find all movies similar as your movie name.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="social-media mt-3">
        <a href="#">
            <i class="fa fa-instagram application"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="#">
            <i class="fa fa-facebook application"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="#">
            <i class="fa fa-twitter application"></i>
        </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center footer-content">Find us on | Instagram | Facebook | Twitter</p>
    <p class="text-center footer-content">Â© 2023 FILM BUFF, A FANDOM COMPANY. All Rights Reserved</p>
</body>

</html>